Mjolicious AJAX demo.

Demonstrates, howto make some AJAX stuff with Mojolicious.

This demo built in git-history style. You can see, 
how it was built step-by-step exploring git commits history 
from beginning to end:

http://github.com/yko/mojolicious-example-ajax/commits/master/

RUN

    script/ajax-example daemon

    open http://localhost:3000/ in browser
